import React, { useState } from 'react' // import Tabs from '@mui/material/Tabs' // import Tab from '@mui/material/Tab' // import Box from '@mui/material/Box' import { currentDate, tomorrowDate, dayAfterDate } from '../util' import './css/TabsForm.css' // import { Tabs, Tab, Typography, Box } from '@material-ui/core' const weekday = ['Sun', 'Mon', 'Tue', 'Wed', 'Thu', 'Fri', 'Sat'] const month = [ 'Jan', 'Feb', 'Mar', 'Apr', 'May', 'Jun', 'Jul', 'Aug', 'Sep', 'Oct', 'Nov', 'Dec' ] function TabsForm () { const [value, setValue] = useState('one') const handleChange = (event, newValue) => { console.log(event) } return (

{weekday[currentDate.getDay()]}

{currentDate.getDate()}

{month[currentDate.getMonth()]}

{weekday[tomorrowDate.getDay()]}

{tomorrowDate.getDate()}

{month[tomorrowDate.getMonth()]}

{weekday[dayAfterDate.getDay()]}

{dayAfterDate.getDate()}

{month[dayAfterDate.getMonth()]}

) } export default TabsForm
